text.section:
The application shall include:
the identity and location of the family child care provider;
an itemization of known and estimated costs;
the total amount of funds required by the family child care provider to comply with State and local regulations;
the funds available to the applicant without financial assistance from the Department;
the amount of financial assistance sought from the Department;
a statement from the family child care provider on how the grant funds will be used;
information that relates to the family income of the grant applicant; and
any other relevant information that the Department requests.
